            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". While there certainly are deals to be found, you might have to hunt harder than before to come across them, and you might need to be quicker at snatching them up. As we’ve highlighted before, there are several factors which have slowed the flow of new cars arriving in the automotive market, which in turn has sent ",
