      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The launch of the Jeep Cherokee L is an important event for Stellantis, considering it adds a 3-row SUV to the Jeep lineup. Sinking $1.6 billion into two existing engine plants, the automaker made a serious investment in the first assembly plant in Detroit opened in the past 30 years.",
