          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "On a more positive note, a new report claims GM is on pace to churn out 26,000 C8 Corvettes for the 2021 model year. That’s not too shabby, considering there have been some serious ",
